{"tid":1058750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 美警搗破 ivy league 收捐獻收生中間人網絡， 大批名人二代在名單之內","createTime":"2019-03-12T17:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T00:57:03.000Z","uid":130105,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f5f7c0f752873f413e486606998fb9898b21f0","tid":1058750,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"睇來， 美警近來好忙吓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n================================<br />\n&bull;Lori Loughlin and husband allegedly 'agreed to pay bribes of $500,000 in exchange for having their two daughters designated as recruits to USC crew'<br />\n&bull;The two girls did not participate in crew, and Loughlin's husband Mossimo Giannulli has also been charged in the scandal <br />\n&bull;Felicity Huffman paid a $15,000 'charitable contribution' 'to participate in the college entrance exam cheating scheme on behalf of her eldest daughter' <br />\n&bull;She knowingly had an individual who was known to assist students or change their answers proctor her eldest daughter's SAT exam according to documents <br />\n&bull;She is charged with Conspiracy to Commit Mail Fraud  as are Loughlin and her husband in the scandal, which has been called Operation Varsity Blues<br />\n&bull;William Rick Singer, the founder of Key Worldwide Foundation, had been identified as the mastermind, and since 2011 has been paid $25M by parents <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/03/12/15/10885192-6799945-image-m-17_1552403376998.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F15%2F10885192-6799945-image-m-17_1552403376998.jpg&h=0f416518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Big house: Full House star Lori Loughlin and Oscar nominee Felicity Huffman are two of the 50 parents charged in a plot to get their children into elite schools (Loughlin with daughters Olivia and Bella in February)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/03/12/15/10885186-6799945-Desperate_housewife_Huffman_paid_a_15_000_charitable_contributio-m-24_1552405071266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F15%2F10885186-6799945-Desperate_housewife_Huffman_paid_a_15_000_charitable_contributio-m-24_1552405071266.jpg&h=104a8d86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Desperate housewife: Huffman allegedly paid a $15,000 'charitable contribution' 'to participate in the college entrance exam cheating scheme on behalf of her eldest daughter' (Huffman and Macy with their daughters Georgia and Sofia at the Golden Globes)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/03/12/16/10891682-6799945-image-a-34_1552409994350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F16%2F10891682-6799945-image-a-34_1552409994350.jpg&h=84f8cb2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Svengali: William Rick Singer (above), the founder of Key Worldwide Foundation, had been identified as the mastermind, and since 2011 has been paid $25M by parents according to filings<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/03/12/16/10888960-6799945-image-m-28_1552407138352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F16%2F10888960-6799945-image-m-28_1552407138352.jpg&h=34751d17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Caught in the act: Huffman and her spouse gave a $15,000 donation to the group that later paid the man who proctored the SAT to her daughter (above)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/03/12/16/10889374-6799945-image-a-33_1552407492208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F16%2F10889374-6799945-image-a-33_1552407492208.jpg&h=9f2f36e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Plan: A recorded phone conversation makes it evident that Huffman is aware that her daughter will be assisted in the test (above)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2019/03/12/16/10888970-6799945-image-m-30_1552407268759.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F16%2F10888970-6799945-image-m-30_1552407268759.jpg&h=c694f2df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Plan: In one call from last year, Huffman revealed she planned to use the same system for her younger daughter (above) after it worked for her older daughter<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/03/12/6545762378336025305/1024x576_MP4_6545762378336025305.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2019%2F03%2F12%2F6545762378336025305%2F1024x576_MP4_6545762378336025305.mp4&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=85cfce80\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2019/03/12/6545762378336025305/1024x576_MP4_6545762378336025305.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6799945/Lori-Loughlin-Felicity-Huffman-implicated-massive-college-entrance-exam-cheating-scandal.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6799945%2FLori-Loughlin-Felicity-Huffman-implicated-massive-college-entrance-exam-cheating-scandal.html&d=fcvOs274DMK6OEArnk0La51QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=2fb7e5fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6799945/Lori-Loughlin-Felicity-Huffman-implicated-massive-college-entrance-exam-cheating-scandal.html</a>"},{"pid":"e7240e083b729ed20b9636c73f57232950e19903","tid":1058750,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T18:17:52.000Z","msg":"英文冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"673ece05d369cc74bdf8f50277435c44ad4b4cce","tid":1058750,"uid":133050,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7240e083b729ed20b